# Normalize line endings to LF in the repo (checked out as-is). Prevents CRLF/LF churn on
# Windows (core.autocrlf) that showed large files as "modified" with no content change and,
# in one case, interacted badly with `git stash` — keep text as LF everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
*.ico binary
